psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer

Class ExperimentEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<Experiment>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.ExperimentEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<Experiment>, ExperimentEnricherListener, AnnotationsChangeListener<Experiment>, ConfidencesChangeListener<Experiment>, ExperimentChangeListener, XrefsChangeListener<Experiment>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExperimentImexEnricherStatisticsWriter

    public class ExperimentEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends EnricherStatisticsWriter<Experiment>
implements ExperimentEnricherListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    01/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
